ðŸ“˜ Description:
You're developing software for a smart dashboard system for modern vehicles.

There are different types of dashboards for:

Electric Cars

Gasoline Cars

Hybrid Cars

All dashboards must:

Display speed

Show fuel or battery level

Sync with a mobile app

Report diagnostic data

But some dashboards also:

Electric Cars: Show charging station availability and battery health

Gasoline Cars: Display fuel efficiency and oil level

Hybrid Cars: Combine both battery and fuel stats, and offer eco-driving tips